@Hostourist-Bcn Apartamento Fira Plaza España is located in the Sants-Montjuïc district of Barcelona, less than 1 km from Sants Railway Station, 2.7 km from Passeig de Gracia and 2.7 km from Palau Sant Jordi. The property is around 2.8 km from Passeig de Gracia Metro Station, 3.1 km from Plaça Catalunya and 3.2 km from Casa Batllo. Free WiFi is available throughout the property and Magic Fountain of Montjuic is less than 1 km away.

The apartment is composed of 3 bedrooms, a fully equipped kitchen, and 1 bathroom. A flat-screen TV is featured. The accommodation is non-smoking.

Camp Nou is 3.2 km from the apartment, while Boqueria Market is 3.4 km away. The nearest airport is Barcelona El Prat Airport, 10 km from @Hostourist-Bcn Apartamento Fira Plaza España.
